### 2. Terminology for Energy Efficiency Network Management
*   **Presenter**: Qin Wu
*   **Slides**: [Terminology for Energy Efficiency  Network Management](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-green-terminology-for-energy-efficiency-network-management-00)
*   **Draft**: [draft-ietf-green-terminology](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-green-terminology/) (v02)
*   Qin Wu outlined updates aiming to align the terminology draft with the framework and YANG modules.
*   Key changes in v02 include:
